# New ports collection makefile for:	m68k-newlib-1.8.1
# Version required:	1.8.1
# Date created:		7 July 1998
# Whom:			Jerry Hicks <jhicks@glenatl.glenayre.com>
#
# $Id: Makefile,v 1.1.1.1 1998/08/09 01:39:04 steve Exp $
